{"tid":1638680,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Apink娜恩遭酸「鼻子又變了」 韓網毒舌洗版：清純臉蛋去哪了","createTime":"2019-10-08T11:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T10:46:13.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a9a7f17d35410f7fb5213636555613b53a670355","tid":1638680,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"南韓女團Apink娜恩能唱能跳，身材火辣又有著美麗臉蛋，受到許多粉絲喜愛。但她自從2018年被發現「修修臉」便深陷整形傳聞，從未正面回應過此事，8日出席活動，新聞照卻引起熱烈討論，下方留言充斥著正、反評論，整形話題再度甚囂塵上。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4426/d4426133.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4426%2Fd4426133.jpg&h=d87e516d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼Apink娜恩8日出席記者會，鼻子似乎又變了。（圖／翻攝自Newsen、xportsnews）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4426/d4426132.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4426%2Fd4426132.jpg&h=14d451f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nApink娜恩8日為了代言商品出席記者會，她穿著白色上衣、牛仔褲，畫著淡妝現身，卻在新聞照刊出後，引來熱烈討論，不少網友認為她的鼻子似乎又不同了，有人留言表示「本來就有著天生美貌了，怎麼會不知滿足呢」、「臉怎麼變那樣，好像別人」、「以前清純的臉蛋去哪了」，但也有人為她發言「明明就滿美的，酸的人不知道長相長得有多好看」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4426/d4426177.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4426%2Fd4426177.jpg&h=01d80e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼Apink娜恩陷整形疑雲，韓網毒舌洗版。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4426/d4426176.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4426%2Fd4426176.jpg&h=cd720e05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事實上，娜恩出道以來有著天生麗質的臉孔，她曾出演節目《我們結婚了》，個性清純、可愛，是許多男生心中的理想型，近年來卻飽受整形問題遭到批評，對此，她曾在《黃金漁場》被問及「你是天生美人嗎」，她坦言「有在管理一點點」，態度坦蕩。"},{"pid":"03da4247fdec7c9e1b6859abb51dafb3c6844cca","tid":1638680,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:34:35.000Z","msg":"已射 樓主一生平安"},{"pid":"c4d6e37cb276497846133039102e1d713e56e0a2","tid":1638680,"uid":40470,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:35:31.000Z","msg":"點解泡菜佬咁天真覺得自己d泡菜妹無整？<br />\n<br />\n定係呃埋自己"},{"pid":"57bd6f473d5e147cdab2456f888155d17bca858a","tid":1638680,"uid":30201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔同咗咁多嘅？"},{"pid":"84bd6171ae1340c2f53bc1d799fa70790a93acb5","tid":1638680,"uid":34643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:40:16.000Z","msg":"呢家先整, 有用咩"},{"pid":"1d1fa097f234a128f6dac4d38afaf41dffa6ec20","tid":1638680,"uid":555,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:40:18.000Z","msg":"我覺得無咩分別 都係咁靚"},{"pid":"5652d7c6fd8cd9dcc9a74fb9297926d7ec75fc9e","tid":1638680,"uid":30201,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/degXoWS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdegXoWS.jpg&h=a0d2e326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我個baby fat娜恩b去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c9e4044f8e345d9af7f821e4955c5fd8125d6c","tid":1638680,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:43:40.000Z","msg":"睇屁蛋得啦，唔洗睇樣"},{"pid":"773b015cae2da9a5f44bbded2a0aa9ea59411123","tid":1638680,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:46:10.000Z","msg":"心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"321293da4cdc1a26f6a2ca890f4576cb57a767e3","tid":1638680,"uid":555,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:48:42.000Z","msg":"超令==<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ySXWExw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FySXWExw.jpg&h=5b487297&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c2960365f35e8b38cd5259cd833e824fe507590","tid":1638680,"uid":56649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:59:23.